## 📋 JWT Testing Checklist

- [ ] Decode and read JWT claims
- [ ] Try `alg: none` attack
- [ ] Brute force weak HMAC secret
- [ ] Check for algorithm confusion (RS256 → HS256)
- [ ] Test JWK injection in header
- [ ] Test JKU/X5U injection pointing to attacker server
- [ ] Test KID injection (path traversal, SQLi)
- [ ] Check if `exp` claim is validated
- [ ] Check if `iat` claim is validated
- [ ] Try modifying `sub`, `role`, `user` claims
- [ ] Test null signature

