## 🧪 Payload Manipulation

```python
import base64
import json

# Decode payload
payload = "eyJ1c2VyIjoiZ3Vlc3QifQ"
decoded = base64.b64decode(payload + "==").decode()
print(decoded)  # {"user":"guest"}

# Modify and re-encode
data = {"user": "admin", "role": "administrator"}
new_payload = base64.b64encode(json.dumps(data).encode()).decode().rstrip("=")
print(new_payload)
```

